Bijou Fernandez https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bijou_Fernandez 0 Bijou Fernandez (born November 4, 1873? – November 7, 1961) was a Broadway actress from New York City.Her theatrical career endured for seven decades, from the 1880s until the mid 20th century. She appeared in a few movies in the silent film era.
